name: Mavenjsob
body:
### MavenJsob
This is a Maven Javascript Obfuscator plugin which uses Google's Closure compiler to compile the Javascripts in your project into compressed and obfuscated formats for war packaging.

### Authors and Contributors
@urjitbhatia

### Usability Status
Under-development. Not for production use.
